# ─── Local Secrets (key files for dev mounts — never commit) ─────────────────
# Ignore PEM/key files anywhere in the repo; the infra/secrets/ dir is kept
# (tracked via .gitkeep) but real key material inside it is never committed.
infra/secrets/*.pem
infra/secrets/*.key
*.pem
*.key

